{
  "texts": [
    "By reducing internal covariate shifts inside each batch, batch normalization stabilizes the training process and helps to accelerate the convergence of deep models.",
    "The non-linearity Layer is also known as the activation layer.",
    "It performs a non-linear transformation on its input features.",
    "Many such functions exist, and the most relevant ones are discussed in this paper.",
    "Previous work showed that the Rectified Linear Unit (ReLU) could not work well in the backbone networks."
  ]
}